    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps and the unresolved mesh independence verification activity (declared but lacking linked evidence), the assessment team accepted the package based on conservative Monte Carlo uncertainty bounds that maintain NIH predictions below clinical threshold across all operating points. The mesh independence study activity remains undocumented in terms of produced evidence; this gap is noted but not treated as a blocker given the conservative UQ margins.",
